  "system": {
    "description": "<p><strong>Trigger:</strong> Creature you can see within 1 Space is targeted by an <strong>Attack </strong>or <strong>Spell Check </strong>that targets its <strong>PD</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Reaction:</strong> You can spend <strong>1 AP</strong>&nbsp;and <strong>1 SP</strong> to become the new target of the Check, and choose to switch places with the original target (if it's willing).</p>\n<p>If the Check is accompanied by a Save (as with a Dynamic Attack Save), you make the Save instead of the original target.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Technique Enhancements</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Steadfast Forbearance:</strong> <strong>(1 SP)</strong> If multiple creatures within 1 Space of you (after switching places if you choose to do so) and are targeted by the same Check, you can attempt to protect them as well. You can spend<strong> 1 SP</strong> per additional target to become the new target of its Check as well. You take the collective damage of all protected creatures against the Check.</li>\n<li><strong>Immense Defense: (2 SP)</strong> You gain Resistance against all damage taken using this Technique.</li>\n</ul>",
